headline: Strong Results Lifted CBRE Group (CBRE) in Q3
summary: Parnassus Investments, an investment management company, released the “Parnassus Value Equity Fund” third quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the third quarter, the Fund (Investor Shares) returned 7.28% (net of fees) underperforming the Russell 1000 Value Index’s 9.43% return.
